{"tid":384600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱「我們只射殺黑人」美白人警被炒","createTime":"2017-09-02T12:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"022eda4dbe2785de1418bf2d00f0eaacc7534aaf","tid":384600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170902/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170902%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=d22c78af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[black]<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">正當美國近年警民衝突不斷，喬治亞州白人老差骨阿博特（Greg Abbott）被拍到在截車路檢時，竟向白人司機表示「我們只射殺黑人」。當地警方調查後，前日宣佈將開除涉事警員，他最終決定退休。<br />\n傳媒上周取得並公開一段2016年7月的汽車紀錄儀片段，可見阿博特夜間在路邊截查可疑醉駕人士時，一名白人女司機表明不敢將雙手放下去拿電話，「我看過很多警方的片段&hellip;&hellip;」。阿博特打斷她說：「但你不是黑人，記着，我們只射殺黑人&hellip;&hellip;你看過的片段是黑人被殺吧？」<br />\n警長雷吉斯特前日表示將開除阿博特，「不論在任何情況下，這些言論都不可原諒和不恰當」，強調對方的言論不代表警局的價值觀。他指當差28年的阿博特一向受人尊敬，但「他做錯了，我不知道當時他的心在想甚麼」。<br />\n<br />\n先行辭職　指言論只為「降溫」<br />\n<br />\n不過，阿博特的代表律師洛魯索指當事人得知將被開除後，前日已自行辭職。洛魯索早前曾指阿博特只是因為遇到不願配合的司機，決定順應對方的言論試圖為情況「降溫」。惟美國全國有色人種協進會（NAACP）批評當地警方的種族歧視問題已根深柢固。<br />\n涉事司機去年夏天曾就醉駕案上庭，其辯護律師布門尼斯近日受訪稱，他去年準備案件時看到上述片段時極為「震驚」，重看多次後不禁想：「不是吧&hellip;&hellip;他以為這只是一個玩笑，但對很多人而言這不是個玩笑。」涉事司機當時被裁定醉駕罪成。<br />\n美聯社/路透社</span>[/black]<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20140013&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20140013%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170902&d=yMFP2zG%2F2ckRvWmh7XTl6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=492482bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20140013%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170902&h=1baf71c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20140013&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170902</a>"},{"pid":"c5e2513856997c52dfbfa1f71785581659030f48","tid":384600,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"055085b13d21be1993f1dc3ac5e0088e508e5c23","tid":384600,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"我聯想左做美女白人警。。。"},{"pid":"bb52dda17a8a305801c2e2d731a34bb20fcce170","tid":384600,"uid":73083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"如果係香港<br />\n個別例子，內部調查，個人行為，最後不了了之<br />\n<br />\n大陸？<br />\n 拉撚左post片既人，完事"},{"pid":"2744a91d370b71c8730eaeb1aa8bd75a436a11bb","tid":384600,"uid":45368,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"稱「我們只射殺黃絲」港警被升職加薪"},{"pid":"f4205d6d26915d41cd4dc96a988ec835984d3deb","tid":384600,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"仲要開得槍就會打晒彈夾冇彈先會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3a0f942f99747f9f5996331978e728ab5f6d12","tid":384600,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"又做假新聞"},{"pid":"69e33668cb7d59780c042eb87d91085748f94db2","tid":384600,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"又黎political correctness"}]}